name: Five Nights at the Silverjew's (final version)
name_original: Five Nights at the Silverjew's (final version)
description: You have been invited over to the house of the Silverjew but he realized shortly after that he ran out of milk so you have to watch over the place while he gets his milk. DO NOT pee on the Silverjew's rug or you will end up like Jimbo after the sex of 1984.
